# Cloudflare Pages routing for the booking host (book.avoqado.io).
#
# Static files (widget.js, book.html, embed.html, _headers) are served as-is
# because file matching wins over rewrite rules. Any other path falls through
# to index.html, which reads the venue slug + optional flow type from
# window.location.pathname.
#
# Examples that resolve to index.html (status 200, URL bar stays clean):
#   /mindform                  → renders booking widget for venue=mindform
#   /mindform/appointments     → same, with flow-type=appointments
#   /mindform/classes          → same, with flow-type=classes
#   /                          → empty-slug fallback (handled in index.html)

